---
alwaysApply: true
---

- This is a Next.js 15 project using the App Router, TypeScript, and Tailwind CSS
- Always use the app/ directory structure, never pages/
- Never use inline styles, always use Tailwind classes
- Brand colors are #315798 (primary blue) and #7D95E0 (light blue), background is #0a0f1a
- All components go in app/components/
- All pages go in app/ as page.tsx files
- Never install unnecessary dependencies, ask first before adding any new package
- Always use TypeScript, never plain JavaScript
- Keep components small and single-purpose
- The site is dark mode only, never add light mode styles
- Never touch globals.css unless explicitly asked
